     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Gruvbox Dark theme. Warm retro earth-tones
         palette (#282828 background, #EBDBB2 foreground, #D65D0E orange accent).
         Beloved by Vim/Neovim users worldwide.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in GruvboxDarkTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

